                    "Title": "邵武 (出生地)",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7442643951db4307af05bc1a1066a902\");'><span id='7442643951db4307af05bc1a1066a902_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1192&endYear=1228')\">1192-1228年</a>，1-37岁</div><div id='7442643951db4307af05bc1a1066a902' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1192&endYear=1210')\">1192-1210年</a>　居乡?<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1211&endYear=1211')\">1211年</a>　隐居故里?尝问学于象山学派包扬（包恢之父），时间不详，姑系于此。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1212&endYear=1228')\">1212-1228年</a>　隐居故里?<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"90210abf90a14da394f10a3f96161297\");'><span id='90210abf90a14da394f10a3f96161297_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1238')\">1231-1238年</a>，40-47岁</div><div id='90210abf90a14da394f10a3f96161297' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>　汀州农民起义失败,福建时局得以暂时稳定。秋尽岁暮，严羽远游返乡,有诗纪乱。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>　远游返乡，感于人生蹭蹬，有诗纪之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>促刺行。<div id='poem_556555' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556555' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556555' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>促刺行</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556555\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556555'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556555'>促刺复促刺，男儿蹭蹬真可惜。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556555'>三年走南复走北，岁暮归来空四壁，邻翁为我长太<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>息。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556555'>人生四十未为老，我已白头色枯槁。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556555'>海内伶俜独一身，裘马摧藏愁欲倒。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556555'>今日饮君数杯酒，座閒颇觉颜色好。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_556555'>忽忆当年快意时，与君笑傲长相期。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_556555'>大杯倒瓮作牛饮，脱巾袒跣唯嫌迟。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_556555'>即今多病筋力弱，壮心虽<span class='inlineComment2'>（夏校本作犹）</span>存兴寂寞。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_556555_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_556555'>君不见昨夜谁为烈士歌，听罢仰空泪零落。</div><div id='poem_sentence_8_556555_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556555'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_1_556555_0'>⑴ 胡本、夏校本作叹</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556555_comment'></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1232')\">1232年</a>　结识戴复古，相交甚笃，时有唱和。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1232')\">1232年</a>　与严仁（字次山）往来甚密，时有唱和。岁末，严仁离乡西去，严羽有诗送行。<span class='label'>作品：</span>送严次山。<div id='poem_556515' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556515' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556515' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>送严次山</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556515\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556515'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556515'>四年栖岭表，三岁客海东。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556515'>人生贵安适，奔走成何功。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556515'>去年喜归来，山花春<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>蒙茸。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556515'>弟侄各捧觞，一笑生华风。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556515'>南山多紫芝，北山多白薇。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_556515'>云空汗漫台，月午生凉辉。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_556515'>俯仰仅一载<span class='inlineComment2'>（夏校本作岁）</span>，脂车复征西。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_556515'>岂以丈夫志，万里犹庭闱。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_556515'>岂以名山川，待公亲品题。</div><div id='poem_sentence_8_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_9_556515'>故园松桂林，一一含贞姿。</div><div id='poem_sentence_9_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_10_556515'>何时赋归来，毋令久凝思。</div><div id='poem_sentence_10_556515_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_11_556515'></div><div id='poem_sentence_11_556515_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556515'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_2_556515_0'>⑴ 原作卷，据林序本、尹本、夏校本改</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556515_comment'></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1232')\">1232年</a>　与李贾（字友山）往来甚密，时有唱和。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1232')\">1232年</a>　与王野（字子文）往来甚密，时有唱和。或于此年作《早春寄潜斋王使君》<div id='poem_556502' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556502' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556502' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>早春寄潜斋王史君</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556502\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556502_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556502'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556502'>昏昏醉睡慵朝起，日日柴门待暖开。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556502_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556502'>春至任从花鸟笑，客来还<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>仗酒樽陪。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556502_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556502'>移舟动觅依江柳，策杖时能访早梅。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556502_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556502'>忽忆使君联骑出<span class='inlineComment2'>（林序本、夏校本作去）</span>，此时乘兴几衔杯。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556502_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556502'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556502_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556502'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_1_556502_0'>⑴ 胡本、夏校本作须</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556502_comment'></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1233&endYear=1233')\">1233年</a>　大概至绍定末，《沧浪诗话》体系方备，基本写成。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1238&endYear=1238')\">1238年</a>　秋冬，悲痛于国家危局，有诗抒怀。<span class='label'>作品：</span>有感（其一）有感（其二）有感（其三）有感（其四）有感（其五）有感（其六）<div id='poem_98773' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_98773' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=98773' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>有感六首<span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其一 </span></a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_98773\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_98773_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_98773'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_98773'>误喜残胡灭，那知患更长。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_98773_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_98773'>黄云新战路，白骨旧沙场。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_98773_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_98773'>巴蜀连年哭，江淮几郡疮。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_98773_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_98773'>襄阳根本地，回首一悲伤。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_98773_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_98773'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_98773_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_556489' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556489' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556489' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其二 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556489_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556489'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556489'>哀痛天灾日，丝纶罪己深。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556489_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556489'>王师曾北伐，胡马尚南侵。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556489_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556489'>谋国知谁计，和亲岂圣心。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556489_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556489'>愿闻修实德，听纳谏臣箴。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556489_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556489'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556489_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_98772' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_98772' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=98772' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其三 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_98772_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_98772'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_98772'>闻道单于使，年来入国频。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_98772_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_98772'>圣朝思息战，异域请和亲。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_98772_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_98772'>今日唐虞际，群公社稷臣。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_98772_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_98772'>不妨盟墨诈，须戒覆车新。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_98772_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_98772'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_98772_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_556490' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556490' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556490' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其四 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556490_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556490'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556490'>灾异时时见，群情恐惧中。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556490_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556490'>修攘今日急，反侧向来同。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556490_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556490'>社稷堪多难，安危系数公。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556490_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556490'>残生江海去，老作一渔翁。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556490_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556490'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556490_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_556491' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556491' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556491' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其五 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556491_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556491'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556491'>陛下春秋盛，谦卑每责躬。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556491_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556491'>得无劳圣虑，犹未定储宫。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556491_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556491'>付托关神器，乾坤在至公。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556491_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556491'>早闻宣诏册，欢喜万方同。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556491_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556491'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556491_comment'></div></div></div><div id='poem_556492' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556492' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556492' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'><span style='margin: 0 0.5em'> 其六 </span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556492_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556492'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556492'>传闻降北将，犹未悔狂图。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556492_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556492'>忍召豺狼入，甘先矢石驱。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556492_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556492'>圣朝何负汝，天意属<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>亡胡。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556492_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556492'>试看山东寇，如今更有无。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556492_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556492'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556492_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556492'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_2_556492_0'>⑴ 林序本、胡本、夏校本作必</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556492_comment'></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1238&endYear=1238')\">1238年</a>　本年末或下年初，严羽卒。<br /></div>"
                },
                {
                    "Latitude": 28.687675,
                    "Longitude": 115.864528,
                    "OffsetLeft": 0,
                    "OffsetTop": 0,
                    "Invisible": false,
                    "RegionId": "CN3601",
                    "Title": "南昌",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b88ab943f2804341adda082a0b8ec856\");'><span id='b88ab943f2804341adda082a0b8ec856_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1228&endYear=1228')\">1228年</a>，37岁</div><div id='b88ab943f2804341adda082a0b8ec856' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1228&endYear=1228')\">1228年</a>　深秋，因汀州农民起义爆发，福建时局激烈动荡，严羽离乡避乱，到达豫章城（今南昌市）<span class='label'>作品：</span>将至浔阳途中寄诸从昆弟。<span class='inlineComment2'>（陈伯海《严羽身世考略》（《上海师大学报》1984年第3期）认为严羽避乱出走的时间当为绍定三年（1230）春天。）</span><div id='poem_556497' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556497' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556497' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>将之<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>①</sup>浔阳途中寄诸从昆弟</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556497\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556497_comment'></div><div class='titleComment'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_title_556497_0'>① 林序本、胡本、夏校本作至</div></div></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556497'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556497'>渺渺孤帆去几程，悠悠天际望湓城。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556497_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556497'>一身避乱辞乡国，千里相思隔弟兄。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556497_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556497'>猿叫匡庐寒暮色，雁过彭蠡带秋声。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556497_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556497'>江湖此去方<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>漂泊，肠断风尘远别情。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556497_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556497'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556497_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556497'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_3_556497_0'>⑴ 林序本、胡本、夏校本作多</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556497_comment'></div></div><br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5f9d4ee6fc8f4dec90816f9a439061b1\");'><span id='5f9d4ee6fc8f4dec90816f9a439061b1_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>，40岁</div><div id='5f9d4ee6fc8f4dec90816f9a439061b1' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>　由衢州取陆返赣。夏秋二季客居豫章城，有诗留别。<span class='label'>作品：</span>豫章留别诸公。<div id='poem_556516' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556516' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556516' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>豫章留别诸公</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556516\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556516'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556516'>登舻<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>眺海日，涉岛听江猿。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556516'>何意豫章国，还著孤蓬根。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556516'>经过徐孺宅，出入洪乔门。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556516'>昔看秋叶落，今见荷花繁。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556516'>颇耽山水趣，正惬朋从温。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_556516'>穷秋催客去，独<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑵</sup>帆若云奔。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_556516'>追攀感数子，酒襟馀泪痕。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_556516'>既伤岁月晚，复恋烟霞樽。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_556516'>欢乐无定序，聚散同朝昏。</div><div id='poem_sentence_8_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_9_556516'>丈夫志四海，别离何足论。</div><div id='poem_sentence_9_556516_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_10_556516'></div><div id='poem_sentence_10_556516_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556516'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_0_556516_0'>⑴ 林序本、胡本、夏校本作楼</div></div><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_5_556516_0'>⑵ 胡本、夏校本作孤</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556516_comment'></div></div><br /></div>"
                },
