                    "Title": "苏州",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4fcc32ba349b409fab8cfd5b167571fe\");'><span id='4fcc32ba349b409fab8cfd5b167571fe_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1228&endYear=1228')\">1228年</a>，37岁</div><div id='4fcc32ba349b409fab8cfd5b167571fe' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1228&endYear=1228')\">1228年</a>　岁暮，南下吴中（今苏州）<span class='label'>作品：</span>避乱途中。<div id='poem_556471' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556471' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556471' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>避乱途中</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556471\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>五言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556471_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556471'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556471'>回首兵戈地，遗黎见几人。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556471_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556471'>他乡空白发，故国又青春。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556471_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556471'>多难堪长客，偷生愧此身。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556471_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556471'>本无匡济略，叹息谩伤神。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556471_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556471'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556471_comment'></div></div></div><br /></div>"
                },
