                    "Invisible": false,
                    "RegionId": "CN3301",
                    "Title": "杭州",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0df643a5c61a48a3842eae2c2a623046\");'><span id='0df643a5c61a48a3842eae2c2a623046_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1229&endYear=1230')\">1229-1230年</a>，38-39岁</div><div id='0df643a5c61a48a3842eae2c2a623046' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1229&endYear=1229')\">1229年</a>　冬末，到达临安。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1230&endYear=1230')\">1230年</a>　客居临安，有诗送赖成之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再送赖成之出都。<div id='poem_556496' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556496' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556496' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>再送赖成之出都</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556496\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'>七言律诗</div></div><div id='poem_title_556496_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556496'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556496'>天际晴霞欲变春，高楼分手泪沾巾。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556496_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556496'>荆吴渺渺孤舟远，江海悠悠白发新。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556496_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556496'>万事蹉跎堪更问，十年离别亦何频。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556496_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556496'>江村几处梅花发，明日相思是旅人。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556496_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556496'></div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556496_comment'></div></div></div><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1230&endYear=1230')\">1230年</a>　客居临安，有诗送吴子才。<span class='label'>作品：</span>钱塘潮歌送吴子才赴礼部。<div id='poem_556546' class='_poem'><div id='poem_title_556546' class='poemTitle showDetail'><a href='/Query.aspx?type=poem1&id=556546' class='poemCommentLink' target='_blank'>钱塘潮歌送吴子才赴礼部</a><a href='javascript: ShowPoemAuthorProfile(25262, \"宋\", \"严羽\", \"poem_title_556546\")'><span class='poemAuthor'><span class='inlineComment1'> 宋·</span>严羽</span></a><br /><div class='titleIndent'></div></div><div id='poem_title_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemContent' id='poem_content_556546'><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_0_556546'>海潮之来自古昔，天下诡观称钱塘。</div><div id='poem_sentence_0_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_1_556546'>东南王气实在此，势与造化为低昂。</div><div id='poem_sentence_1_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_2_556546'>观其映日始一线，何处群鹭纷然翔。</div><div id='poem_sentence_2_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_3_556546'>渐闻鼓声震原野，疑是三军嚣阵行。</div><div id='poem_sentence_3_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_4_556546'>银城天际忽过眼，卷蹴厚地何仓皇。</div><div id='poem_sentence_4_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_5_556546'>馀波已去洒月窟，怒气犹自吹扶桑。</div><div id='poem_sentence_5_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_6_556546'>百川倒流号<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑴</sup>呼汹，天吴河伯神皆竦。</div><div id='poem_sentence_6_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_7_556546'>海上长人出水惊，巨鳌辟易三山动。</div><div id='poem_sentence_7_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_8_556546'>广陵之涛安可比，吴客雄誇徒为尔。</div><div id='poem_sentence_8_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_9_556546'>请君看此凭江楼，载酒无劳棹小舟。</div><div id='poem_sentence_9_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_10_556546'>湖上百花春荡目，笙箫<span class='inlineComment2'>（林序本作歌）</span>聒我非清游。</div><div id='poem_sentence_10_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_11_556546'>洪涛万里壮可吞，笔底飒飒洪涛奔。</div><div id='poem_sentence_11_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_12_556546'>愿持忠愤愬明主，一第于君何足论。</div><div id='poem_sentence_12_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_13_556546'>钱塘日边云气多，君之行兮莫蹉跎。</div><div id='poem_sentence_13_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_14_556546'>教人临期<sup class='reference inlineComment2'>⑵</sup>奈别何，赠君钱塘海潮歌。</div><div id='poem_sentence_14_556546_comment'></div><div class='poemSentence' id='poem_sentence_15_556546'></div><div id='poem_sentence_15_556546_comment'></div></div><div class='poemNote' id='poem_note_556546'><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_6_556546_0'>⑴ 林序本、尹本、夏校本作浩</div></div><div class='inline1'><div id='poem_sentence_14_556546_0'>⑵ 林序本、夏校本作岐</div></div></div><div id='poem_note_556546_comment'></div></div><br /></div>"
